title: United Kingdom Imports - Residues & Waste From The Food Inds. Prepared
description: Imports - Residues & Waste From The Food Inds. Prepared in the United Kingdom decreased to 247.55 GBP Million in September from 280.24 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports - Residues & Waste From The Food Inds. Pre in the United Kingdom averaged 137.14 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 318.20 GBP Million in May of 2022 and a record low of 42.08 GBP Million in July of 2000. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Residues & Waste from The Food Inds. P.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
